name: Sexy Stockings Collection LoRA
description:
A LoRA for creating different types and variations of stockings and knee-high socks.

If you feel like supporting my work, please consider visiting my Patreon to get access to more detailed instructions on how to get the most out of my models and have a say in what's up next: Link.

A very versatile LoRA that can produce many variations and types of stockings:

Check the trigger words for reference. All of them can be combined freely, some better than others. I had a lot of fun playing around with this and discovering different combinations.

I haven't tested this in conjunction with other LoRAs, but if you do, let me know how it goes.

Recommended LoRA strength is around 0.7.

Based on UberRealisticPornMerge

If you like this you might also like my other LoRAs.
